{"tid":148498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傳真社：內地一直參與高鐵總站內地口岸區設計】","createTime":"2017-03-08T15:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T13:32:47.000Z","uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dcfb4c44b678a0e9e46603b699dfbac9518eb4","tid":148498,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/638801359645269/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F638801359645269%2F&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=0fe80338\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/638801359645269/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df880104beb823c434607aec1508c078e35761cd","tid":148498,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7889b266e9940a578dc7dc0143875faa6c7ecc84","tid":148498,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"按內地要求度身訂造間隔 高鐵內地口岸區半年前已動工<br />\nMarch 8, 2017<br />\n<br />\n傳真社 FactWire<br />\n<br />\n(傳真社香港8日電) - 明報星期一公開高鐵西九龍總站內地口岸區的平面圖則，詳細顯示站內一地兩檢的內地設施。運輸及房屋局回應僅指該份圖則並非最新版本，強調仍與內地商討一地兩檢的憲制問題。傳真社取得另一份於2016年7月修訂的設計圖則文件，文件顯示中方在出入境設施的設計上高度參與，細緻度及至「衛生間」內佈局、房間牆壁厚度等。傳真社獲曾參與工程項目的消息人士確認，圖則曾呈交內地鐵路部門審批，港方早在去年9月根據圖則展開「內地口岸區」工程，內牆間隔已大致完成。<br />\n <br />\n傳真社取得高鐵西九龍總站一份名為「廣深港高鐵內地口岸區佈局方案」的設計文件，是2016年7月修訂版本。設計圖則沒有顯示接收方，但整份文件採用簡體字，並用上「人工通道」、「衛生間」及「邊檢洗漱間」等內地用語，部分有英文簡稱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/03/08/%E6%8C%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%BA%A6%E8%BA%AB%E8%A8%82%E9%80%A0%E9%96%93%E9%9A%94-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsingle-post%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%259A%2594-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25B7%25A5&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=68d6c4ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/03/08/%E6%8C%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%BA%A6%E8%BA%AB%E8%A8%82%E9%80%A0%E9%96%93%E9%9A%94-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%A5</a>"},{"pid":"a3f6080c71f4f8f45bd8fc075512ad07a25841d3","tid":148498,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ca6bf357d0899e6d5266c2e8680b36ba8aae3c","tid":148498,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"實施一地兩檢不違基本法 涂謹申：港可撥部西九站份土地予內地<br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵預計明年中落成，惟西九總站實施一地兩檢問題仍未有定案。立法會議員涂謹申認為可撥歸部份土地予內地政府，以免出現內地人員在港執法情況，惟現屆政府無法給予市民信心，始令執行上有困難。<br />\n涂謹申今早接受電台訪問時指，在西九站內實施一地兩檢，法律及技術上均可行，香港可將該處幾千呎土地撥歸內地政府，等於縮少香港領土範圍，此做法可避免抵觸《基本法》有關內地人員不能在港執法的條文。惟涂謹申表示「主要係信心問題」，因現屆政府無法給予市民信心可有效執行一地兩檢，市民亦會擔心開此先例後，香港會否「一路縮細」，但長遠而言，涂認為可落實一地兩檢。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員田北辰則建議在高鐵站內劃出口岸區予內地人員執法，包括拘捕權，他指乘客選坐高鐵均是返回內地，應先心理準備遵守內地法律。出席電台節目的理工大學土木及結構工程學系副教授熊永達指，西九站內的內地人員不需要有拘捕權，認為可參考航空公司做法，拒絕被列入不受歡迎名單的旅客登車或原車遣返等方法，解決日後的出入境問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/76421/%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95-%E6%B6%82%E8%AC%B9%E7%94%B3-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%AF%E6%92%A5%E9%83%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E7%AB%99%E4%BB%BD%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%88%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F76421%2F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%25B6%2582%25E8%25AC%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2592%25A5%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=5c8aae5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/76421/%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95-%E6%B6%82%E8%AC%B9%E7%94%B3-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%AF%E6%92%A5%E9%83%A8%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E7%AB%99%E4%BB%BD%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%88%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n涂謹申, 民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f72ed4d44f341604b186381c44d5aa158808f62","tid":148498,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"大陸就大陸啦，乜鬼嘢內地"},{"pid":"d99d5a5ea752289b0667489350e62d12af437356","tid":148498,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"你搞得一地兩檢點會唔問支那意見呀"},{"pid":"ea517c9e4f7e7cd768da9bcde7be9cabf1c6c803","tid":148498,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸就大陸啦，乜鬼嘢內地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有線條標題嚟"},{"pid":"11d644e4f5c044f88bc11bef813c05840d199b7f","tid":148498,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"